  "text": "This section is organized as follows: Sect. 4.1 discuss the minimum energy routing. Next, we build a linear programming with relaxed energy constraint to approximate the original problem (OR-D). Based on this relaxed problem, a near optimal solution is constructed in Sect. 4.3. Finally, Sect. 4.4 summarizes our solution. [CITATION_1] show that with enough total-energy and appropriate transfer efficiency, the minimum energy routing would outperform others. As we can meet these conditions, we define the minimum energy routing as the routing scheme.",
